    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="切换镜像"><a href="#切换镜像" class="headerlink" title="切换镜像"></a>切换镜像</h4><p><strong>方法一</strong>： 修改 composer 的全局配置文件（推荐方式）<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 切换到国内镜像</span></span><br><span class="line">composer config -g repo.packagist composer https://packagist.phpcomposer.com</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 删除国内镜像，恢复到默认镜像</span></span><br><span class="line">composer config -g repo.packagist composer https://packagist.org</span><br><span class="line">或</span><br><span class="line">composer config -g --unset repos.packagist</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><a id="more"></a><p><strong>方法二</strong>：修改当前项目的 composer.json 配置文件：<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">composer config repo.packagist composer https://packagist.phpcomposer.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>方法三</strong>：修改配置文件<br>文件位置：1. 当前项目<code>composer.json</code>; 2.或全局文件 <code>~/.comspoer/comspoer.json</code><br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">"repositories"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"packagist"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"type"</span>: <span class="string">"composer"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"url"</span>: <span class="string">"https://packagist.phpcomposer.com"</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h4 id="忽略php版本错误"><a href="#忽略php版本错误" class="headerlink" title="忽略php版本错误"></a>忽略php版本错误</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 安装</span></span><br><span class="line">composer install --ignore-platform-reqs</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 更新</span></span><br><span class="line">composer update --ignore-platform-reqs</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 添加单个包</span></span><br><span class="line">composer require --ignore-platform-reqs --prefer-dist yiisoft/yii2-httpclient</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
